data.description:
Price Change!! Former Model home.  Large and spacious home featuring 4 bedrooms, 3 full baths.  Closet space galore in 3 of the bedrooms.   Large windows throughout with shutters for privacy.  Beautiful tile in main living areas with carpet in the right places.  Walk up the staircase with Brazilian cherry style wood railing to a loft that can become anything your life desires. (Playroom, office, etc.).  Kitchen completes with granite counters  
 Once you have toured the interior walk out to the patio where you will be welcomed by a fenced in pool and a very large yard.  Make it your oasis.. Use your imagination and 
 Welcome to your new home!!  Home has been very well lived in and needs some TLC Seller is very motivated. Sold as Is
